      "segments": [
        "s0"
      ],
      "start": 9.84,
      "text": "It is currently 14 degrees and cloudy in Berlin-Tempelhof."
    },
    {
      "end": 17.76,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 14.88,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "adef89dd539",
        "ad86a6d6389"
      ],
      "end": 41.91,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3",
        "s4"
      ],
      "start": 19.02,
      "text": "Competition in frontier AI models is shifting toward high-fidelity sensory output and agentic tooling. MiniMax has released Speech 2.8, an update to its voice technology designed for more natural and lifelike vocalizations. At the same time, Nous Research has introduced the Photon iMessage Hermes Agent to expand its suite of open-model tooling."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a9ddb4e5ccf",
        "a69cf1182f5"
      ],
      "end": 63.6,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s5",
        "s6",
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 42.13,
      "text": "This push for realism is particularly evident in the rapid iteration of Chinese video models. Alibaba Cloud is now promoting its Wan video generation models for users to create AI videos. Kuaishou's Kling AI continues to showcase similar high-fidelity video generation capabilities."
    },
    {
      "end": 66.02,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s8"
      ],
      "start": 63.6,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 71.0,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 66.34,
      "text": "This afternoon will bring rain with temperatures between 14 and 16 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 73.3,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 71.36,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 73.681,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s11"
      ],
      "start": 73.3,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 74.3,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s12"
      ],
      "start": 73.681,
      "text": "[very very long pause before speaking; then mature adult voice, most emotional, strong, warm, radiant, deeply encouraging; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    }
  ],
